title: Vegafe - Augustijonu Str.
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Asian, Fusion
description: Offers daily specials with one vegan meal, marked, alongside other vegan options. Range juices and smoothies. A large portion of the menu items are Asian inspired (Indian and Chinese). Has English menu. Will pack your order for take-away. Pasties and cakes for sale at the counter. Rustic setting with an alternative and upmarket feel.
